---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { Separator } from "../components/ui/separator";
---

<BaseLayout title="About – Christopher Klint" description="Engineering leader with experience across telecom, digital signage, and e-commerce. From fullstack developer to Director of Technology, now Staff Engineer at Telness Tech.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">About</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
      I'm an engineering leader who loves building products and growing teams. My career has taken me from coding bootcamp graduate to directing technology strategy, and I bring that full-stack perspective to everything I do.
    </p>

    <Separator className="my-8" />

    <div class="space-y-10">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold">Experience</h2>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-8">
          <div class="relative border-l-2 border-muted pl-6">
            <div class="absolute -left-[7px] top-1 h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold">Staff Engineer</h3>
              <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Apr 2025 &ndash; Present</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-primary">Telness Tech &middot; Stockholm</p>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li>Increased integration speed with new network operators by 80%, enabling faster onboarding and market launches</li>
              <li>Designed and shaped new APIs and architected end-to-end product capabilities across the platform</li>
              <li>Evaluated and drove decisions on new systems, tools, and commercial proposals for long-term scalability</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="relative border-l-2 border-muted pl-6">
            <div class="absolute -left-[7px] top-1 h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold">Director of Technology & Innovation</h3>
              <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Aug 2024 &ndash; Mar 2025</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-primary">Nenda &middot; Stockholm</p>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li>Defined a strategic technology roadmap resulting in 100%+ YoY growth</li>
              <li>Enabled new revenue streams through Digital Signage, designed modularly for SaaS and advertising models</li>
              <li>Cut Azure cloud costs by 50% through instance right-sizing and logging optimizations</li>
              <li>Reduced project delivery times by 75%, accelerating product-to-market timelines</li>
              <li>Regularly engaged with CEO, investors, and strategic stakeholders on technology direction</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="relative border-l-2 border-muted pl-6">
            <div class="absolute -left-[7px] top-1 h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold">Engineering Manager</h3>
              <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Aug 2023 &ndash; Aug 2024</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-primary">Telness Tech &middot; Stockholm</p>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li>Managed and mentored a team of 10 engineers, scaling the tech department to 50+</li>
              <li>Led the external API project, gaining international interest after launch</li>
              <li>Delivered critical features enabling customer launches and 100%+ YoY growth</li>
              <li>Reduced new engineer onboarding time &mdash; deploying their own code within 20 days</li>
              <li>Awarded <strong class="text-foreground">Role Model of the Year</strong> by company-wide vote (2023 & 2024)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="relative border-l-2 border-muted pl-6">
            <div class="absolute -left-[7px] top-1 h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold">Fullstack Developer</h3>
              <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Dec 2021 &ndash; Aug 2023</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-primary">Telness Tech &middot; Stockholm</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              Built and maintained cloud-based BSS/OSS platform features using TypeScript, React, Go, and AWS. Contributed to the core telecom infrastructure enabling mobile operators worldwide.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative border-l-2 border-muted pl-6">
            <div class="absolute -left-[7px] top-1 h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold">Fullstack Developer</h3>
              <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Feb 2021 &ndash; Dec 2021</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-primary">Bencha &middot; Stockholm</p>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li>Owned the web application built with Next.js, React, and TypeScript with sub-2-minute CI/CD deployments</li>
              <li>Built AI-driven features including image-based clothing search using machine learning</li>
              <li>Collaborated on product innovation including platform gamification</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="relative border-l-2 border-muted pl-6">
            <div class="absolute -left-[7px] top-1 h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold">Software Engineer Intern</h3>
              <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Dec 2020 &ndash; Feb 2021</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-primary">Viabl Ventures &middot; Remote</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              Built a client portal using Django and Vue.js with Atomic component architecture for improved modularity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <Separator className="my-2" />

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold">Education</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
          <div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold">Stockholm University</h3>
              <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">2015 &ndash; 2018</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Bachelor's Degree, Business Administration</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              Chair of the International Committee, Business Manager for the Silicon Valley Project, active in Föreningen Ekonomerna.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold">Springboard</h3>
              <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">2020 &ndash; 2021</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Software Engineering Career Track</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              700+ hours of hands-on course material covering front-end, back-end, databases, and data structures &amp; algorithms. Completed 4 portfolio projects with 1:1 industry expert mentorship.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <Separator className="my-2" />

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold">Languages</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-muted-foreground">
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">English</strong> &mdash; Native / bilingual</li>
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">Swedish</strong> &mdash; Native / bilingual</li>
          <li><strong class="text-foreground">Danish</strong> &mdash; Full professional proficiency</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
